viewData.name: HP 15.6" OMEN 15-dc0030nr Laptop
viewData.short_description: Buy HP 15.6" OMEN 15-dc0030nr Laptop featuring 2.2 GHz Intel Core i7-8750H Six-Core, 16GB DDR4 | 1TB 7200 rpm HDD + 128GB SSD 15.6" FHD 1920 x 1080 IPS Display. Review HP
viewData.long_description: Play your favorite PC games while on the go with the HP 15.6" OMEN 15-dc0030nr Laptop. The OMEN features an HP sandblasted hairline brushing finish and a carbon fiber pattern in shadow black. There is also a four-zone RGB lighting backlit keyboard with a numeric keypad.
